org.smtlib

Interface ISort.IApplication

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IAccept, IPos.IPosable, ISort
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Sort.Application
    Enclosing interface:
    ISort

    public static interface ISort.IApplication
extends ISort
    The interface for a Sort expression that consists of either an arity 0 sort symbol or a positive-arity symbol with the appropriate number of arguments.
